Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位于横川·轻井泽之间的碓冰岭是国铁最险的路段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初修铁路的时候用的是阿伯特齿轨式铁轨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:11:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在两轨正中间加上一条锯齿状的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让机车的齿轮咬合于上  用以爬坡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只有旧线路留着这种轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺带一提  这里的最大坡度可达千分之66.7
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这啥意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指的是每走1000米  高度就会上升66米
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这点么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩泉  才不是这么点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对铁路而言是极陡的坡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今天作为特别培训  要让你们驾驶这辆辅助机车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早点搞定早吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别扫兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是ED42吗  我还以为要开EF63
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢这么老的家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪敢哪敢  十分荣幸！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,急行「白山」号是由车头3台ED42型电力机车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:12:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中间夹着8节客车  加上车尾的1台组成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我绷紧神经  好好驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  现在来决定由谁坐在车尾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  尾部机车可是最难控制的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不事先商量好时间安排和警笛信号的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就尽力别拖后腿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊  那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶座果然很不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能在这里展现我的驾驶才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  接下来是下坡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  那个乱七八糟的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧  樱井那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚是要把主干控制器归零的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？速度在变快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须使用电制动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我不知道怎么操作制动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看说明书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:14:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  小海  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵的尾部机车好像在推着我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱井吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  我给她发下信号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱井那家伙在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在开玩笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  快进行制动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你那边在磨磨蹭蹭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去速度只会不断变快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种情况下继续制动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中间的车厢会被挤歪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定会脱线的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:15:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君  速度升得好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  正在想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山  速度是不是在变快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话  会出大事故的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样  只能赌一把了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是国铁引以为傲的模拟训练程序  做的不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静下来  好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为公安队…不  作为国铁人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们全都忘记了最重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个事故是由你们全员造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是不太适合公安队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且  还是代理班长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就快下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…我抽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  又抽到乌龟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快  轮到高山君你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说有话说  是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公安队的制服  我倒觉得挺合适你的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  现在在我面前的高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,样子有点不太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得高山君只要相信自己就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且警四的成员人都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札沼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你担心了  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札沼很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能理解别人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚成田先生来过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明天的实习先不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为依照现在的情况也出不了什么成绩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天大家一起出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为放松精神去逛街吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得来轻井泽一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错诶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  也叫上岩泉君和小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邀请樱井的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是代理班长的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  好难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（明天，我们要去轻井泽街上走走，樱井也一起来吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为听说全是实习
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没带什么过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是匆忙买的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  很适合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  岩泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.43,0:18:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全找不到好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是只知道吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是接受意大利菜的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近有个很好的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  就那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.94,0:18:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我就没有什么要说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道无论札沼穿什么都很可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不是什么夸奖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  樱井呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然也邀请了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿能早点和好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  警四打来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假期很愉快吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭田小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打断你们的休假不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我有件事情要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望高山君能去迎接一个重要人物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方似乎指名一定要高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  去纪念礼拜堂就可以了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事件了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  只是被拜托了一点小事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不是什么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完事了就去找你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.96,0:19:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱井可能不久就到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要是联络我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让她去你们那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就回来  待会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱井
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（我刚到轻井泽）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她过来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  我没问小海他们的目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.17,0:20:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  没有人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱井
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小遥他们没和你一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到樱井也会穿这种衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗  我又不是讨厌这种
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  为什么特意来教会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底准备干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  那个  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.24,0:21:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.12,0:21:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本是想能在工作上帮帮忙才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在这种没人的教会与小葵见面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.40,0:21:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  还撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我万万没想到会是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撒谎是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊  必须要说明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是说是和高山君两个人碰面的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.30,0:22:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么连樱井和小海都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在陡坡区间运行时  为给列车补充上下坡时的牵引力和制动力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.18,0:23:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而加挂的机车就是补机
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.08,0:23:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活跃在信越本线横川-轻井泽间  协助列车翻越碓冰岭峰的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.20,0:23:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国铁ED42型电气机车可谓经典代表
